Get Team records by year

cfb_records.Rd

Get Team records by year

cfb_records(year, team = NULL, conference = NULL)

Arguments

year

Year (*Integer*, 4 digits YYYY, optional)
team

Team - Select a valid team, D1 football (*String*, optional)
conference

Conference Name - select a valid FBS conference (*String*, optional) Conference Names P5: ACC, Big 12, Big Ten, SEC, Pac-12 Conference Names G5 and FBS Independents: Conference USA, Mid-American, Mountain West, FBS Independents, American Athletic

Examples
